{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addToggleRef","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"notify"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GToggleNotify","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This functionality is intended for binding ","type":"text"},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to a proxy"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object managed by another memory manager. This is done with two","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"paired references: the strong reference added by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"text":" and a reverse reference to the proxy","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"object which is either a strong reference or weak reference.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The setup is that when there are no other references to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"only a weak reference is held in the reverse direction from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to the proxy object, but when there are other references held to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":", a strong reference is held. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" callback is called"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the reference from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":" to the proxy object should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“toggled” from strong to weak ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"is_last_ref"},{"type":"text","text":" true) or weak to strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"code":"is_last_ref","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" false)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Since a (normal) reference must be held to the object before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the initial state of the reverse"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"link is always strong.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Multiple toggle references may be added to the same gobject,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"however if there are multiple toggle references to an object, none","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of them will ever be notified until all but one are removed.  For","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this reason, you should only ever use a toggle reference if there"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is important state in the proxy object.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that if you unref the object on another thread, then ","type":"text"},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" might","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"still be invoked after ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and the object argument","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"might be a dangling pointer. If the object is destroyed on other threads,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you must take care of that yourself."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"type":"text","text":" must be released with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and another reference is established."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"]]},"metadata":{"title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GLibObject","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolPAAE12addToggleRef6notify4datayySvSg_SpySo8_GObjectVGSgs5Int32VtXCSg_AGtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:10GLibObject0B0C","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify","text":"GToggleNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/object\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object/ObjectProtocol-Implementations":{"title":"ObjectProtocol Implementations","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object\/objectprotocol-implementations","kind":"article"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject","abstract":[],"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"GLibObject","type":"topic"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object":{"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"Object","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The base object type."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object/addToggleRef(notify:data:)":{"type":"topic","title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and another reference is established."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"addToggleRef","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GToggleNotify","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)"}}}